ated To</th>\n			<td style=\"padding:3px;border:1px solid #ccc;\">$events-crmid$</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<th style=\"width:20%;text-align:left;padding:3px;border:1px solid #ccc;font-weight:100;\">Contact List</th>\n			<td style=\"padding:3px;border:1px solid #ccc;\">$events-contactid$</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<th style=\"width:20%;text-align:left;padding:3px;border:1px solid #ccc;font-weight:100;\">Location</th>\n			<td style=\"padding:3px;border:1px solid #ccc;\">$events-location$</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<th style=\"width:20%;text-align:left;padding:3px;border:1px solid #ccc;font-weight:100;\">Description </th>\n			<td style=\"padding:3px;border:1px solid #ccc;\">$events-description$</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<div>$detail_link_text_en$<br />\n </div>\nThanks & Regards,<br />\n$creator_name$<br />\n<span style=\"color:rgb(178,34,34);\">------------ </span><br />\n<span style=\"color:rgb(178,34,34);\">This email is sent automatically from <a href=\"http://crm.cloudpro.vn\">CRM system</a>. Please do not reply!</span>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<p></p>\n', 0, 1, 'Users');
