 style=\"color:rgb(178,34,34);\">------------ </span><br />\n<span style=\"color:rgb(178,34,34);\">This email is sent automatically from <a href=\"http://crm.cloudpro.vn\">CRM system</a>. Please do not reply!</span>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<p></p>\n', 0, 1, 'Users');
